{"tid":1694130,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Face ID 面部辨識有漏洞   13 歲以下兒童有可能繞過 Face ID 的保護","createTime":"2019-11-05T03:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T00:50:48.000Z","uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"46631e4210360c687f36aef98d334683eb62cf25","tid":1694130,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"自從 iPhone X 在 2017 年推出後，Apple 就開始在旗艦 iPhone 型號以 Face ID 面容辨識技術，取代以往的 Touch ID 指紋辨識技術。早前韓國就發生了一宗與 Face ID 被誤用的事件，一名使用 iPhone X 的父親因此「被消費」了近 1,000 萬韓圜（約 67,561 港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyFZ-EmiPhQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQyFZ-EmiPhQ&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=06f9f1b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyFZ-EmiPhQ</a><br />\n<br />\n該名父親金先生讓就讀小學四年班的兒子使用自己的 iPhone X，結果兒子的臉成功通過 iPhone X 的 Face ID 認證，在 App Store 購買了大量遊戲物品。在接受韓國 JTBC 電視台的新聞訪問時，金先生表示發現信用卡有接近 1,000 萬韓圜的海外簽帳消費，仔細檢查後發現是兒子購買遊戲的支出。<br />\n<br />\n金先生指自己利用 Face ID 鎖定 iPhone，但系統卻將兒子的臉誤當成他的臉，將手機解鎖和認證消費。他嘗試向 Apple 以求退款，但不得要領。韓國電視台表示，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">類似個案在 2017 年 iPhone X 推出後亦曾經在美國發生，Apple 之後在官網新增風險提示，指跟 iPhone 用戶長相相似的 13 歲以下兒童，有可能繞過 Face ID 的保護。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n來源：JTBC"},{"pid":"3b2658e7196a8db8aae54f7a770a5a577f6dfedd","tid":1694130,"uid":158977,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"Fake news.<br />\nios好安全 apple冇奶共"},{"pid":"6576d7683a8ff85506ddf5acf35aade21ecc71c1","tid":1694130,"uid":25656,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:35:14.000Z","msg":"自己課咗金想退錢下話"},{"pid":"a5cb397e43b0c7873c6d120c404a4ae0c3bc183b","tid":1694130,"uid":109923,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3b2658e7196a8db8aae54f7a770a5a577f6dfedd","tid":1694130,"uid":158977,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"Fake 